text: Two Guys from Milwaukee is a 1946 American comedy movie directed by David Butler and starring Dennis Morgan, Jack Carson, Joan Leslie, Janis Paige, Rosemary DeCamp. It was distributed by Warner Bros. and was followed up in 1948 by Two Guys from Texas. ==Other websites== * * Category:1946 comedy movies Category:American comedy movies Category:Warner Bros. movies Category:Movies directed by David Butler
title: Two Guys from Milwaukee
